      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; simulation setup reviewed by senior analyst.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by a second analyst for boundary condition correctness and material property assignment. Formal use-error assessment not required at MRL 2. No simulation setup errors identified during peer review."
    },
    {
