      "rationale": "CFD inlet flow rates, rotational speeds, and fluid viscosity set to match experimental conditions within measurement uncertainty bands reported by Morrison et al. (2016). Inlet velocity profiles derived from upstream pipe flow at matched Reynolds number. Fluid temperature maintained at 37°C in both experiment and simulation. Equivalency confirmed by sensitivity analysis showing NIH variation of < 3% across the uncertainty range of each input parameter."
