    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the project credibility plan. Primary validation demonstrates NIH predictions within 9.3% of FDA benchmark data with correct worst-case rank ordering. Secondary validation against the Giersiepen (1990) dataset corroborates the hemolysis model constants. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 is satisfied at all five CPB operating points. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for this Class II CPB device.",
